snippet.title: SECRET CROSSING DYA - SIDE STORY PART 1, FULL VERSION.
snippet.description:
Hi! I'm back with latest update about StoryTaco's latest game, SECRET CROSSING. 

DYA's birthday on 18/08!!

SECRET CROSSING is now available on Apple App Store : https://apps.apple.com/my/app/secret-crossing-story-game/id6443592667

SECRET CROSSING is now available on Google Play Store : https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.storytaco.p23client&hl=en&gl=US

Seems like this game bringing a new concept gameplay this time. It might be take time to understand the whole game especially the tasks and others.
